  "remarks": "Olga Burova has been the so-called “First Deputy Minister of Culture of the Republic of Crimea” since 15 May 2023. In that role, she has promoted Crimea as a centre of Russian culture and as a part of Russian history, and supported its illegal annexation by Russia in 2014.",
